com.compendium.core.datamodel
Class Model

java.lang.Object
  com.compendium.core.datamodel.Model
All Implemented Interfaces:
IModel, java.io.Serializable
public class Model
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, IModel

Model Class is the base class for the object cache for a given database and also holds a set of the database service objects and project level preference settings.

  • Compendium data objects
  • Database service objects
  • User Profile object
  • Method to generate Unique IDs based on the timestamp and IP address combination
  • Project level preference settings
